		<div class="post" id="post-2713222">
		<div class="long">
			<div class="head">
									<div class="options">
						<a href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,2713222)" class="btn btn-default btn-small btn-sm">Fold</a>
					</div>
								<div class="title" id="post-title-2713222">
																		
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dolphinslugchugger" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1969477); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1969477&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610164583" alt="DolphinSlugchugger" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1969477)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dolphinslugchugger" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1969477); return false;" >DolphinSlugchugger</a></span> <span class="odate time_1482345565 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">21 Dec 2016 18:39</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2713222">
									

<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;Feels&#32;a&#32;lot,&#32;and&#32;I&#32;mean&#32;a&#32;LOT&#32;like&#32;</span><a href="/scp-885-j">SCP-885-J</a>.<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;Though&#32;there&#32;are&#32;funny&#32;moments,&#32;at&#32;times&#32;you're&#32;just&#32;fission&#32;for&#32;yaks,&#32;especially&#32;with&#32;an&#32;inconsistent&#32;and&#32;heavy&#32;handed&#32;&quot;hilarious&quot;&#32;reaction.</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;Then&#32;you've&#32;got&#32;the&#32;object&#32;class.&#32;I&#32;personally&#32;love&#32;it;&#32;it&#32;sets&#32;the&#32;tone&#32;with&#32;the&#32;nonstandard&#32;object&#32;class&#32;by&#32;telling&#32;is&#32;its&#32;intrinsic&#32;nature&#32;is&#32;&quot;Loud&#32;and&#32;messy.&quot;&#32;The&#32;loud&#32;part,&#32;however,&#32;is&#32;not&#32;meaningfully&#32;expounded&#32;upon&#32;by&#32;Yerry's&#32;nature,&#32;as&#32;any&#32;mention&#32;of&#32;his&#32;volume&#32;is...&#32;&quot;loud.&quot;&#32;Compare&#32;to&#32;your&#32;messy&#32;class,&#32;which&#32;is&#32;backed&#32;up&#32;by&#32;him&#32;leaving&#32;dead&#32;bodies&#32;everywhere,&#32;spreading&#32;his&#32;metabolic&#32;waste&#32;products,&#32;etc.</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;Of&#32;particular&#32;note&#32;is&#32;footnotes&#32;9&#32;and&#32;10.&#32;There&#32;you've&#32;got&#32;a&#32;beautiful&#32;example&#32;of&#32;showing&#32;something&#32;which&#32;furthers&#32;the&#32;roommate's&#32;frustration&#32;and&#32;then&#32;go&#32;ahead&#32;and&#32;tell&#32;us&#32;how&#32;to&#32;feel&#32;as&#32;well.&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;To&#32;be&#32;honest,&#32;most&#32;of&#32;the&#32;footnotes&#32;don't&#32;contribute&#32;much&#32;of&#32;meaning.&#32;Footnote&#32;1&#32;you&#32;might&#32;have&#32;something&#32;good&#32;with&#32;&quot;dropping&#32;dem&#32;[sic]&#32;gram&#32;negs&#32;everywhere,&quot;&#32;But&#32;how&#32;is&#32;he&#32;loud?&#32;In&#32;what&#32;way?</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;Footnote&#32;2's&#32;</span><em>very</em><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;good.&#32;This&#32;is&#32;the&#32;only&#32;true&#32;evidence&#32;that&#32;Yerry's&#32;loud,&#32;and&#32;it&#32;also&#32;tells&#32;us&#32;the&#32;general&#32;nature&#32;of&#32;his&#32;loudness.&#32;I&#32;like&#32;it.</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;Footnote&#32;3's&#32;general&#32;idea&#32;is&#32;good,&#32;but&#32;execution&#32;leaves&#32;me&#32;feeling&#32;&quot;meh.&quot;&#32;The&#32;class-c&#32;amnestics&#32;bit&#32;covers&#32;everything&#32;you&#32;need,&#32;but&#32;might&#32;need&#32;different&#32;phrasing.&#32;'Dr.&#32;Mike's&#32;request&#32;for&#32;bi-weekly&#32;class-c&#32;amnestic&#32;administrations&#32;is&#32;currently&#32;pending.'&#32;or&#32;some&#32;such&#32;thing.&#32;This&#32;shows&#32;the&#32;promiscuity&#32;of&#32;the&#32;bacteria&#32;and&#32;reinforces&#32;just&#32;how&#32;bad&#32;it&#32;is.</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;Footnote&#32;4&#32;is.&#32;Bad.&#32;It's&#32;a&#32;stupid&#32;name&#32;by&#32;it's&#32;nature,&#32;and&#32;if&#32;you&#32;just&#32;put&#32;it&#32;in&#32;quotation&#32;marks&#32;the&#32;whole&#32;object&#32;we'd&#32;get&#32;that&#32;idea.</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;Footnote&#32;5&#32;is&#32;a&#32;bit&#32;contrary&#32;to&#32;the&#32;idea&#32;it's&#32;footnoting.&#32;The&#32;anecdote,&#32;sans&#32;'He&#32;eats&#32;EVERYTHING,'&#32;is&#32;humorous&#32;enough,&#32;but&#32;suggests&#32;a&#32;bit&#32;more&#32;ravenous-than-usual&#32;appetite&#32;which&#32;should&#32;appear&#32;on&#32;the&#32;documentation,&#32;mostly&#32;for&#32;the&#32;sake&#32;of&#32;leaving&#32;its&#32;truth&#32;up&#32;in&#32;the&#32;air&#32;while&#32;still&#32;being&#32;descriptively&#32;accurate.</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;Footnote&#32;6&#32;is&#32;topical,&#32;includes&#32;a&#32;catchphrase-esque&#32;introduction,&#32;and&#32;just&#32;communicates&#32;frustration&#32;over&#32;lost&#32;money&#32;in&#32;a&#32;bland&#32;way.&#32;The&#32;sentence&#32;it&#32;footnotes&#32;communicates&#32;this&#32;very,&#32;very&#32;well;&#32;a&#32;followup&#32;sentence&#32;in&#32;the&#32;actual&#32;SCP,&#32;possibly&#32;involving&#32;a&#32;request&#32;for&#32;remuneration&#32;by&#32;Dr.&#32;Mike&#32;to&#32;Yerry&#32;for&#32;christmas,&#32;also&#32;communicates&#32;what&#32;Mike&#32;lost&#32;beyond&#32;losing&#32;that&#32;money.</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;Footnote&#32;7&#32;sucks.&#32;The&#32;fact&#32;they're&#32;puns&#32;communicates&#32;their&#32;base-level&#32;humor,&#32;and&#32;we&#32;get&#32;that&#32;Yerry&#32;shouldn't&#32;be&#32;able&#32;to&#32;talk.&#32;It's&#32;the&#32;job&#32;of&#32;the&#32;Foundation,&#32;even&#32;in&#32;-J's,&#32;to&#32;explain&#32;what's&#32;happening.&#32;It's&#32;nonsensical&#32;by&#32;nature.&#32;We&#32;don't&#32;need&#32;Mike's&#32;thoughts&#32;on&#32;how&#32;nonsensical&#32;it&#32;is.</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;Footnote&#32;8&#32;is&#32;just.&#32;Useless.&#32;We&#32;get&#32;it.&#32;Mike's&#32;upset.&#32;Where&#32;the&#32;fuck&#32;do&#32;the&#32;rats&#32;go?&#32;Putting&#32;a&#32;number&#32;on&#32;exactly&#32;how&#32;many&#32;rats&#32;might&#32;also&#32;make&#32;us&#32;more&#32;sympathetic&#32;to&#32;Mike.</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;So&#32;onto&#32;the&#32;actual&#32;text.&#32;It's&#32;mostly&#32;pretty&#32;good;&#32;I&#32;only&#32;take&#32;real&#32;issue&#32;with&#32;two&#32;sentences.&#32;First&#32;is&#32;&quot;The&#32;entity&#32;occasionally&#32;invites&#32;that&#32;fucking&#32;weird&#32;dude&#32;with&#32;the&#32;mask&#32;to&#32;&quot;hang&#32;out&quot;&#32;and&#32;smoke&#32;dat&#32;dank&#32;shit,&#32;leaving&#32;that&#32;godawful&#32;smell&#32;on&#32;everything.&quot;&#32;Why&#32;isn't&#32;&quot;dat&#32;dank&#32;shit&quot;&#32;in&#32;quotation&#32;marks?&#32;049&#32;makes&#32;sense,&#32;and&#32;absolutely&#32;helps&#32;the&#32;humor,&#32;but&#32;why&#32;&quot;fucking&#32;weird&quot;?&#32;The&#32;second&#32;is&#32;&quot;SCP-1347-1353-J&#32;is&#32;currently&#32;involved&#32;in&#32;a&#32;romantic&#32;relationship&#32;with&#32;████&#32;██████,&#32;who&#32;is&#32;very&#32;loud&#32;during&#32;promiscuous&#32;activities.&quot;&#32;Again,&#32;don't&#32;tell&#32;us&#32;that&#32;she's&#32;loud.&#32;You've&#32;almost&#32;or&#32;actually&#32;communicated&#32;this&#32;with&#32;&quot;A&#32;total&#32;disregard&#32;for&#32;Yerry's&#32;roommates&#32;while&#32;they&#32;are&#32;sleeping.&quot;&#32;in&#32;a&#32;much&#32;better&#32;way.</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;Tl;Dr&#32;It's&#32;mediocre,&#32;and&#32;while&#32;there&#32;are&#32;scraps&#32;which&#32;show&#32;what&#32;it&#32;could&#32;become,&#32;it&#32;ultimately&#32;lacks&#32;in&#32;execution.&#32;-1&#32;for&#32;now,&#32;but&#32;it's&#32;close&#32;to&#32;being&#32;</span><em>good</em><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">.</span></p>

							</div>

								
					
